Architecture (high level)

Code: GitHub (mono or multi-repo)

CI/CD: GitHub Actions or Jenkins

Registry: Amazon ECR

IaC: Terraform (provision) + Ansible (post-provision bootstraps)

Runtime: Docker + Amazon EKS (managed K8s)

Deploy: Argo CD (GitOps) + Helm charts (dev/stage/prod)

Ingress: AWS Load Balancer Controller → ALB

Data: Amazon RDS (Postgres) / ElastiCache (optional)

Logs: Fluent Bit → CloudWatch Logs

Metrics/Tracing: Prometheus + Grafana (+ optional Datadog APM)

Secrets: AWS Secrets Manager + KMS

Notifications: Slack/Email (SNS → Slack webhook)


org/
├─ app/                        # application source (e.g., Node/Go/Java)
│  ├─ Dockerfile
│  └─ k8s/ (local dev only)
├─ infra/                      # Terraform mono-repo
│  ├─ modules/ (vpc, eks, rds, ecr, alb, iam, s3_logs)
│  └─ envs/
│     ├─ dev/
│     ├─ stage/
│     └─ prod/
├─ ops/                        # Ops config & bootstraps
│  ├─ ansible/
│  ├─ observability/ (prom, grafana, dashboards)
│  └─ logging/ (fluent-bit)
└─ gitops/                     # Argo CD apps & Helm charts
   ├─ charts/myapp/
   │  ├─ templates/
   │  ├─ values.yaml
   │  ├─ values-dev.yaml
   │  ├─ values-stage.yaml
   │  └─ values-prod.yaml
   └─ apps/ (Argo CD Application manifests per env)
